rows.label: qev090603_MSG0001
rows.name: This is where that xeno said we could find the Ganglion.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090603_MSG0002
rows.name:
Hmm... But I don't see anything.
No Ganglion, no captives...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090603_MSG0004
rows.name: Noble fools like you make for the easiest sort of prey.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090603_MSG0005
rows.name:
I am Stalio. I suppose you can think of me
as a colleague of sorts.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090603_MSG0006
rows.name: Except where you hunt creatures, I hunt primitives like you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090603_SEL0011
rows.name: Laugh at Stalio and her empty words.

rows.label: qev090603_SEL0021
rows.name: Say that only a coward relies on such cheap tricks.

rows.label: qev090603_MSG0007
rows.name:
You humans are such a dim race.
No understanding of your place at all.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090603_MSG0008
rows.name:
You exist only to be used, killed, and cast aside.
You are but puppets for my pleasure.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090603_MSG0009
rows.name:
A typical primitive response.
Will you threaten to kill me next?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090603_MSG0010
rows.name:
It makes no difference.
Pray if you will, for your empty lives end here.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090603_MSG0013
rows.name:
Your hubris rings hollow.
It's fear that drives the weak to deception![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090603_MSG0014
rows.name:
I'll see that fear realized a hundredfold.
No xeno will see mercy from me![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev090603_MSG0015
rows.name: One last pathetic wail before death. Now...let the hunt begin![ST:wait ]
